{{!-- How it works --}}
<section id="how">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow">How it works</div>
    <h2>Three steps to a loaded device.</h2>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-glyph">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 14h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-7a9 9 0 0 1 18 0v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-1a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Connect a device</h3>
        <p>Plug in your Shokz headphones or any USB storage device. Conduxor detects it and gets ready to sync.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-glyph">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 18V5l12-2v13"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="16" r="3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Browse your library</h3>
        <p>View albums and imported audio from your Music library, or browse any folder on your Mac.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-glyph">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>One-click sync</h3>
        <p>Check any audio file to copy it to the selected device. Uncheck to remove it. That's the whole interaction.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

